<h3 class="text-center">In your opinion, what is most important in  a relationship?</h3>
<h5>Rank your preferences from top to bottom:</h5>


<ul class="list-inline">
  <li id="cardinal" class="element-tag"> My significant other has a lot of initiative</li>
  <li id="fixed" class="element-tag"> Me and my partner must be on the same page. That's it!</li>
  <li id="mutable" class="element-tag"> My partner is very flexible and usually adapts to my wishes.</li>
</ul>



<%= simple_form_for(current_user, url: profiles_mode_rankings_path) do |f| %>
  <%= f.input  :mode_ranking, as: :hidden %>
  <%= f.submit 'Continue', class:'button' %>
<% end %>

